    <bioghist id="md5-8fdaee06afc672a10fbfbbdbd525a642" encodinganalog="1.7B">
      <note>
        <p>Percilla Groves was a charter member of Local 2 of the Association of University and College Employees, an independent union founded on feminist principles.  She served as the library representative on the first and second AUCE Local 2 contract committees and chaired the committee at various times.  As of 2003, she is a librarian at SFU.  <lb/><lb/>An autobiographical sketch is available in the hard copy version of the finding aid maintained in the Archives Reading Room.</p>
      </note>
    </bioghist>
