    </odd>
    <scopecontent encodinganalog="1.7D">
      <p>The fonds consists of three notebooks that pertain to the negotiation of a first contract between AUCE Local 2 and the University, negotiation for subsequent contracts, the strike of 1979, and the formation of a teaching assistant's union. Also includes four photographs and a t-shirt.</p>
    </scopecontent>
    <arrangement encodinganalog="1.8B13">
      <p>The files were arranged by the archivist.</p>
    </arrangement>
